14
00:01:23,760 --> 00:01:24,630
Miaomiao.

15
00:01:24,680 --> 00:01:25,520
Please, calm down.

16
00:01:26,760 --> 00:01:28,480
Miaomiao!

17
00:01:28,680 --> 00:01:30,240
