23
00:01:37,400 --> 00:01:38,240
Miaomiao.

24
00:01:38,640 --> 00:01:40,240
Come over first, please. Okay?

25
00:01:40,240 --> 00:01:41,320
Miaomiao, come over.

26
00:01:41,320 --> 00:01:42,920
I'll explain everything to them.

27
00:01:43,240 --> 00:01:44,760
I don't want to see her.

28
00:01:45,840 --> 00:01:47,400
Tell her to leave.

29
00:01:47,400 --> 00:01:48,960
