- Now!

30
00:01:49,280 --> 00:01:51,320
I'll ask her to go.

31
00:01:56,800 --> 00:01:58,040
Miaomiao.

32
00:02:03,520 --> 00:02:04,440
It's alright now.

33
00:02:06,000 --> 00:02:06,840
It's all fine now.

34
00:02:16,760 --> 00:02:17,600
Xibei.

35
00:02:18,600 --> 00:02:19,760
Say what's on your mind.

36
00:02:20,320 --> 00:02:21,280
Um…

37
00:02:21,280 --> 00:02:22,840
Boss, he…

38
00:02:26,280 --> 00:02:28,400
