50
00:02:51,000 --> 00:02:51,840
I admit it.

51
00:02:52,160 --> 00:02:53,440
That day, I was emotional.

52
00:02:53,440 --> 00:02:54,960
Got a little carried away.

53
00:02:57,640 --> 00:02:59,200
Don't forget that agreement we singed

54
00:02:59,200 --> 00:03:00,440
before joining Keep Love.

55
00:03:00,960 --> 00:03:02,320
No dating allowed.

56
00:03:02,760 --> 00:03:04,600
But Boss is dating more than any of us.

57
00:03:04,600 --> 00:03:05,440
What can I say?

58
00:03:06,240 --> 00:03:07,400
Hopeless.

59
00:03:11,920 --> 00:03:13,640
Xibei.

60
00:03:14,480 --> 00:03:15,840
Xibei.

61
