Have some water.

62
00:03:33,800 --> 00:03:34,640
Brother.

63
00:03:36,760 --> 00:03:38,440
Did you really marry Ding Daang?

64
00:03:41,960 --> 00:03:42,800
So you don't have to

65
00:03:43,480 --> 00:03:45,360
