74
00:04:08,560 --> 00:04:11,360
including the time, place, and items.

75
00:04:11,800 --> 00:04:13,640
You recall them perfectly.

76
00:04:14,440 --> 00:04:15,920
Like reciting from a textbook.

77
00:04:17,080 --> 00:04:19,480
But I can't feel any warmth
from you anymore.

78
00:04:21,200 --> 00:04:22,520
The way you look at me feels like

79
00:04:22,520 --> 00:04:24,000
