84
00:04:51,840 --> 00:04:52,800
Can you forgive me?

85
00:05:00,800 --> 00:05:01,840
I'll make sure

86
00:05:04,160 --> 00:05:06,520
Hu Yitong comes back to you.

87
00:05:08,360 --> 00:05:09,800
That's my promise to you.

88
00:05:13,480 --> 00:05:14,320
Trust me.

89
00:05:30,400 --> 00:05:31,240
Ruomai.

90
00:05:33,120 --> 00:05:35,000
Do you think I'm being foolish?

91
00:05:37,040 --> 00:05:38,720
I was ready for all of this.

92
00:05:41,440 --> 00:05:44,000
But my heart still aches so much.

93
00:05:47,920 --> 00:05:50,280
He's like ice that never warms.

94
00:05:51,640 --> 00:05:52,840
Every time

95
