103
00:06:17,480 --> 00:06:18,760
Stop drinking.

104
00:06:20,400 --> 00:06:22,320
He's not worth it.

105
00:06:22,920 --> 00:06:24,760
He's like a heartless AI.

106
00:06:25,480 --> 00:06:27,680
Men's passion never lasts.

107
00:06:28,440 --> 00:06:29,800
Don't let yourself get stuck again.

108
00:06:29,800 --> 00:06:30,760
Pull yourself together.

109
00:06:33,440 --> 00:06:35,080
He's not some AI.

110
00:06:35,800 --> 00:06:36,920
He's no AI.

111
00:06:37,720 --> 00:06:39,120
He's my Aming.

112
00:06:43,400 --> 00:06:44,640
Stop drinking!

113
00:06:46,000 --> 00:06:47,080
I'll take you home.

114
00:06:47,080 --> 00:06:48,520
I'm not going home.

115
00:06:49,240 --> 00:06:50,560
I have no home.

116
00:06:51,240 --> 00:06:52,280
I have no home.

117
00:06:53,120 --> 00:06:54,280
I have no home.

118
00:06:55,200 --> 00:06:56,320
I have no home!

119
00:06:58,240 --> 00:06:59,240
I have no home.

120
00:07:04,920 --> 00:07:07,720
Go and bring my Aming back right now.

121
00:07:08,080 --> 00:07:09,000
Bring Aming back to me.

122
00:07:09,000 --> 00:07:10,000
Did you hear that?

123
00:07:10,000 --> 00:07:10,880
Hurry up!

124
00:07:11,060 --> 00:07:12,160
Find him and bring him here.

125
00:07:12,760 --> 00:07:13,600
I'm on it.

126
00:07:14,160 --> 00:07:15,880
My passion can last forever.

127
00:07:16,280 --> 00:07:19,120
Even love gurus
lose their touch sometimes.

128
00:07:26,440 --> 00:07:28,480
Would you risk everything
to love someone?

129
00:07:32,200 --> 00:07:33,040
I would.

130
00:07:33,790 --> 00:07:34,680
Why?

131
00:07:34,800 --> 00:07:36,160
Because I met the right person.

132
00:07:36,880 --> 00:07:38,200
What makes someone the right one?

133
00:07:39,960 --> 00:07:41,440
Someone who can unlock my code.

134
00:07:43,280 --> 00:07:45,640
What if she's someone empty inside?

135
00:07:45,920 --> 00:07:46,860
I'll fill it with love.

136
00:07:48,600 --> 00:07:49,760
