138
00:07:58,560 --> 00:07:59,480
I'll keep going.

139
00:08:07,800 --> 00:08:08,640
Ding Daang.

140
00:08:08,840 --> 00:08:10,000
How did you drink this much?

141
00:08:10,440 --> 00:08:11,800
