172
00:11:40,160 --> 00:11:41,000
Miaomiao.

173
00:11:42,040 --> 00:11:43,720
I was really nervous yesterday.

174
00:11:45,080 --> 00:11:46,560
If you had really fallen down...

175
00:11:50,880 --> 00:11:51,720
Hmm?

176
00:11:52,560 --> 00:11:53,440
Afraid of losing me?

177
00:11:55,040 --> 00:11:55,880
Yeah.

178
00:11:57,520 --> 00:11:58,720
Are you afraid of losing me?

179
00:12:00,760 --> 00:12:01,600
I am.

180
00:12:31,000 --> 00:12:32,290
During the contract period,

181
00:12:33,040 --> 00:12:33,880
Party B

182
00:12:34,800 --> 00:12:35,640
