while watching a sad movie♪

200
00:14:00,760 --> 00:14:03,740
♪Some endings cannot be changed♪

201
00:14:03,960 --> 00:14:09,910
♪They don't belong in sweet memories♪

202
00:14:11,290 --> 00:14:17,050
♪I've already lost you♪

203
00:14:17,050 --> 00:14:22,530
♪Thinking of it takes my breath away♪

204
00:14:22,830 --> 00:14:28,780
♪The movie ends, so many couples around♪

205
00:14:28,780 --> 00:14:33,560
♪Yet none were ever like us♪

206
00:14:34,670 --> 00:14:38,700
♪The past will always pass♪

207
00:14:39,030 --> 00:14:46,610
♪If you could still hold me tight
in your arms♪

208
00:14:47,080 --> 00:14:50,330
♪I'd believe
that there are miracles in love♪

209
00:14:50,890 --> 00:14:56,540
♪I'd prove
that I'm still in love with you♪

210
00:14:59,000 --> 00:15:02,530
♪I've learned how to cherish
what we had♪

211
00:15:02,530 --> 00:15:08,790
♪But sadly, it's not you♪
